Subject: [PATCH 6.6 427/568] PCI: rockchip: Use GPIOD_OUT_LOW flag while requesting ep_gpio
Date: Tue, 30 Jul 2024 17:48:54 +0200
Message-ID: <20240730151656.557703817@linuxfoundation.org>
